tiers.ability_description: Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
The first time each Scoundrel ally uses a Basic ability on their turn, reset their cooldowns and gain 100% Turn Meter. Limit once per character per battle.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever an enemy is defeated by a Scoundrel ally, that enemy can't be revived.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever Dark Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
The first time each Light Side ally reaches 75%, 50%, and 25% Health grant them Protection Up (50%) for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled or prevented.
Whenever Light Side allies gain a buff, they recover 2% Health and Protection.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
At the start of their first turn, Empire allies gain Offense equal to 400% of their current Defense. Then they lose 50% Defense.
Whenever Dark Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
The first time each Dark Side ally reaches 90%, 70%, and 50% Health inflict Doubt on a random enemy that doesn't have it for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled or prevented.
At the start of their first turn, Empire allies gain Offense equal to 400% of their current Defense. Then they lose 50% Defense.
